## Subject Verification (metadata method per env constraints)
Per env constraints, LoremFlickr `<keywords>` ARE the subject metadata.
- `penthouse?lock=42`: keyword "penthouse" -- residential property type, not cityscape. OK.
- `balcony?lock=77`: keyword "balcony" -- residential property feature, not cityscape. OK.
- `oceanview?lock=99`: keyword "oceanview" -- property view descriptor, residential context. OK.

Note: single-keyword queries confirmed to return distinct images (all 3 have different MD5 hashes). Multi-keyword comma queries returned a single fallback image (LoremFlickr caching behavior) -- used single keywords instead.

